decks.notes: This deck focuses on using ramp spells and Eldrazi creatures to control the game and overwhelm the opponent with powerful threats. By utilizing mana acceleration, card draw, and removal spells, the goal is to quickly bring out big Eldrazi creatures like Emrakul, the Promised End and World Breaker to dominate the battlefield. The deck also includes disruptive cards like Karn, the Great Creator and Kozilek's Return to disrupt the opponent's game plan and maintain control of the game. Overall, the strategy revolves around ramping into big threats and out-valuing the opponent.
